{"type": "article", "id": 15794, "title": "组合插座", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-09T07:35:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 269, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135549pS5rAG1C6Zh7wdP8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款可以拼接的插座满足现在的人们对插座的多样需求。除了传统的三孔插座和供手机充电的 USB 接口，它还可以接上蓝牙音响，LED 灯，网线接口甚至 WiFi 连接器。它们像积木一样拼接起来，衍生出无数个不同的版本，而可以调整的长短和次序还能适应不同的环境。由于模块化的设计，这款插座能根据用户需要定制特殊插口。<a href=\"http://casitoo-powerstrip.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261431353WNTcK59ldZ7kfPX.gif\" width=\"1050\" height=\"591\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143138BOWyKInxZEh4oC6s.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"591\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143138dJiTxZ8Yeh3OWCUP.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"591\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143139aGHNTe3zxmFdCikA.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"591\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}